                    <span>However Amazon writes "by Humberto Maturana" we cannot forget the other writer (Francisco Varela) dead about three years.<P>Both come from the research started by Stafford Beer in Chile and they are not alone: People as Terry Winograd or Fernando Flores are in the same package and all of them give powerful reasons against the so-called GOFAI (Good-Old-Fashioned-Artificial-Intelligence).<P>Maturana and Varela are not the first but, for sure, they are among the brightest.</span>
                  
